<section class="py-20 px-8 max-w-[1440px] mx-auto">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
    <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-surface-container-low p-16 rounded-xl group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all duration-500 border border-white/5">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-5xl mb-12" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">language</span>
      <h4 class="font-headline text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Sites profissionais</h4>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xl max-w-md">Desenvolvimento de plataformas que não apenas existem, mas convertem visitantes em clientes através de design editorial.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-16 rounded-xl group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all duration-500 border border-white/5">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-5xl mb-12" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">developer_board</span>
      <h4 class="font-headline text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Sistemas</h4>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xl">Softwares internos desenhados especificamente para o fluxo da sua equipe.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-16 rounded-xl group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all duration-500 border border-white/5">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-5xl mb-12" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">psychology</span>
      <h4 class="font-headline text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Consultoria</h4>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xl">Direcionamento técnico para quem sabe onde quer chegar mas busca a ferramenta ideal.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-primary-container p-16 rounded-xl group transition-all duration-500 border border-white/5 flex flex-col justify-between">
      <div>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary text-5xl mb-12" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">autorenew</span>
        <h4 class="font-headline text-4xl font-bold text-on-primary mb-6">Automação de processos</h4>
        <p class="text-on-primary-container text-xl max-w-md">Elimine tarefas repetitivas e deixe que a tecnologia trabalhe por você enquanto foca no que realmente importa.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
